cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "BioMate-KB Bioconductor Skills"
abstract: >-
  Top 100 Bioconductor packages by official download score, formatted as
  Claude Code Skills (Anthropic SKILL.md format) with structured decision-support
  fields: when-to-use, best practices, key parameters, common pitfalls, result
  interpretation, and alternatives. Designed for use with Claude Code agents in
  bioinformatics workflows.
authors:
  - name: BioMate
    website: https://biomate.ai
type: dataset
keywords:
  - bioconductor
  - bioinformatics
  - claude-code
  - claude-skills
  - rna-seq
  - single-cell
  - differential-expression
  - skill-library
license: CC-BY-4.0
